SETBONUSDURATION

NAME
        SetBonusDuration()

SYNOPSIS
        int SetBonusDuration(int i)

DESCRIPTION
        Specifies the number of heartbeats that should elapse before a bonus's effects wear off.

EXAMPLES
        SetBonusDuration(100)

LOCATION
        /lib/bonus


SEE ALSO
        SetPoints, SetSkills, SetStats

Author
        Cratylus

